net.opentsdb.query.expression

类 NumericFillPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.query.expression.NumericFillPolicy

  • public class NumericFillPolicy
extends Object
    POJO for serdes of fill policies. It allows the user to pick either policies with default values or a scalar that can be supplied with any number.
    从以下版本开始:
    2.3
